{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation()","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>Animation()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>El constructor <strong><code>Animation()</code></strong> de <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a> devuelve una instancia del objeto <code>Animation</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>animation</em> = new Animation([<em>effect</em>][, <em>timeline</em>]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parámetros","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"effect\"><code>effect</code>&nbsp;<span class=\"badge inline optional\">Opcional</span></dt>\n <dd>El efecto objetivo, es un objeto de la interfaz <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffectReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ,para asignarlo a la animación. Aunque en el futuro podrían ser asignados otros efectos como <code>SequenceEffect</code> o <code>GroupEffect</code>, el único efecto disponible actualmente es <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Este puede ser <code>null</code> (valor por defecto) para indicar que no debe aplicarse ningún efecto.</dd>\n <dt id=\"timeline\"><code>timeline</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Opcional</span></dt>\n <dd>Especifica el&nbsp; <code>timeline</code> con el que asociar la animación, como un objeto de tipo basado en la interfaz <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> . Actualmente el único tipo de línea de tiempo disponible es <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, pero en el futuro habrá lineas de tiempo asociadas , por ejemplo, con gestos o desplazamiento. El valor por defecto es <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, pero puede ser establecido en <code>null</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/eJyWzm/?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Follow the White Rabbit </a>, el constructor <code>Animation()</code> es usado para crear una <code>Animation</code> para el <code>rabbitDownKeyframes</code> utilizando el <code>timeline</code> del documento:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> rabbitDownAnimation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>rabbitDownKeyframes<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timeline<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-animation\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation()' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Editor's draft.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.Animation","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El constructor Animation() de Web Animations API devuelve una instancia del objeto Animation.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Animation.Animation()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/animation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/animation/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation","title":"Animation()"}],"pageTitle":"Animation() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}